quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,"(Oh men! Your obsession to attain, hoard and show off) opulence diverts you (and keeps you busy)"
  102,2,Right until you land in (your) graves
  102,3,"No, surely not! You shall soon find out"
  102,4,"Again, be sure! You shall soon find out"
  102,5,"No, of course not! If you only knew with certainty"
  102,6,You shall surely see hell
  102,7,"Then, you would really see it with the eye of certainty"
  102,8,"And then, you would certainly be called to account for the blessings and the bounties"